                Manual level layout in a 3D dungeon is tedious and inconsistent. The <code class="font-mono text-[#00FFC8] text-sm bg-[#00FFC8]/10 px-1 rounded">Editor/LevelBuilder/</code> directory contains nine tools that cover the full layout workflow — from placing individual prefabs to distributing groups of objects and auditing components across the scene.
